279
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:04,875
Hanya basah karena hujan.

280
00:24:06,958 --> 00:24:09,916
Kau cukup bertanggung jawab
sampai mengejarku.

281
00:24:10,458 --> 00:24:12,708
Aku khawatir kau pingsan di jalan.

282
00:24:14,125 --> 00:24:16,208
